### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/

### Create college
POST http://localhost:8000/colleges
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test College"
}

### Create student
POST http://localhost:8000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "college_id": 1,
  "roll_number": "COL001",
  "name": "Student One",
  "email": "s1@example.com"
}

### Create event
POST http://localhost:8000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "college_id": 1,
  "title": "Data Science Workshop",
  "event_type": "Workshop"
}

### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/events/1/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "student_id": 1 }

### Attendance
POST http://localhost:8000/events/1/attendance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "student_id": 1, "status": "present" }

### Feedback
POST http://localhost:8000/events/1/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{ "student_id": 1, "rating": 5, "comment": "Great!" }

### Event stats
GET http://localhost:8000/reports/event/1/stats

### Event popularity (filter by event_type optional)
GET http://localhost:8000/reports/event-popularity?college_id=1&event_type=Workshop

### Student participation
GET http://localhost:8000/reports/student-participation?college_id=1

### Top active students
GET http://localhost:8000/reports/top-active-students?college_id=1&limit=3
